QuestData.Title: Frenzy Fang
QuestData.Description:
<You remove a fully-grown fang from the fallen frenzy.
You have heard of some seafaring groups that made weapons or decorations out of fangs found in the deeps, perhaps your new allies could find use for this?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Frenzy Fang to Artisan Itanu in Mezzamere in Nazjatar.
